                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390513-1497-offence-1 t18390513-cd-27"></join>16th of April</rs>, 3 loaves of bread, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 3<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18390513-name-205" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-205" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
